City: search each row of the csv for a match
if match is city or city alias, set matchedLocString to "city=New York" (for example)
if match is state, set matchedLocString to "state=NY"
show option 'search in New York, NY'
This version of search makes no material contribution to Yup. It serves as an implementation of
basic city/state searching, for the purpose of personal practice and demonstration.
In the future, I will focus strictly on features that contribute to the project.
